name: [ felicitas est ingratum ]
description:
~ ungrateful happiness ~
.
.
"I desire loneliness once again,
I desire chaos in an organized disorder,
I desire hatred from whom I loved,
I desire to let down...

when I see the sky, I can't see happiness raining down,
the thunder slaps my silence, conflicted unwittingly,
and then tomorrow comes at my doorway, offering a little hope...

does it matter now?"
--140615
.
.
Graphite and colored pencils on paper, with digital touch.
2300 x 2300 pixel.
